Marie Goreth Nyiraminani (27 Kamena 1981), ni umupasiteri w'umunyarwandakazi ufite ubumuga bwo kutumva no kutavuga, yabayeho agearageza guharanira ko bagenzi be babaho bishimye<ref name=":0">https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/29119</ref>. Ni umuhanzi akaba kandi akora umwuga wo kwita ku misatsi muri rusange.

== Ubuzima bwe ==
Marie Goreth Nyiraminani yavutse 27 Kamena 1981 avukana ubumuga bwo kutumva no kutavuga we na murumuna we.<ref name=":0" /> Mu 1994 muri Jenoside yakorewe abatutsi yabuze mama we na barumuna be babiri naho basaza be batutu baburirwa irengero, Nyiraminani yasigaranye na Se bajya mu bugande<ref name=":0" />. 

== Umwuga ==


Marie Goreth Nyiraminani yize amashuri ye abanza mu ishuri ry'abafite ubumuga bwo kutumva no kutavuga ahahoze hitwa Butare mu ntara y'amajyepfo akomereza mu gihugu cya  Kenya aho yigiye amasomo y'igihe gito mu ishuri rya bibiriya.<ref name=":0" /> Asoje amasomo yafunguye urusengero rw'abafite ubumuga bwo kutumva no kutavuga i Kigali. Nyiraminani ni umuhanzi akaba anakora umwuga wo gusokoza imisatsi bimufasha mu mibereho ye ya buri munsi hamwe na murumuna we nawe ufite ubwo bumuga.<ref name=":0" />

